<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>DATA<sp/>=<sp/>1<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">#<sp/>通用数据通道</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>VIDEO<sp/>=<sp/>2<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">#<sp/>视频流</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>AUDIO<sp/>=<sp/>3<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">#<sp/>音频流</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>CUSTOM<sp/>=<sp/>4<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">#<sp/>自定义应用通道</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
