<sect1 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_a_p_i___r_e_f_e_r_e_n_c_e_1autotoc_md114">
<title>工具函数</title><sect2 id="md_client__sdk_2docs_2_a_p_i___r_e_f_e_r_e_n_c_e_1autotoc_md115">
<title>async detect_nat_type(stun_server: str, stun_port: int) -&gt; NATType</title><para>独立的 NAT 类型检测函数。</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".py"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">from</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>p2p_sdk<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">import</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>detect_nat_type</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">nat_type<sp/>=<sp/>await<sp/>detect_nat_type(</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>stun_server=</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;stun.l.google.com&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>stun_port=19302</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><bold>参数：</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>stun_server</computeroutput> (str): STUN 服务器地址</para>
